✨ We heard you, Tams! ✨

We’ve been a little quiet lately — kasi busy kami formulating more flavors just for you (and your cravings 🤭).
And this Monday, we’re finally dropping something NEW:
🍪 Biscoff Tiramisu — fresh, creamy, and ready to be your next favorite! 🤎
💚 This is Tamu 🍰
Your all-time cravings, made better:
🍌 Banana Pudding
☕🍫 Classic Tiramisu
🍪 Biscoff Tiramisu (NEW!)
We always listen to your suggestions, and now we’re bringing them to life — fresh batches, improved taste, and premium ingredients. ✨
⚠️ Note: We usually bake 100 pcs per week, but we can only accomodate 65 pcs only, if you’re eyeing a bulk order, message us early — slots fill up fast.
📦 Available Stocks:
– 20 pcs Classic Tiramisu (Kittii size)
- 5 pcs Classic Tiramisu (tobi size)
– 5 pcs Biscoff Tiramisu (Kittii size)
– 32 pcs Banana Pudding (Kittii size)
– 3 pcs Banana Pudding (Tobi size)
📍 Pick-up points: FEU 🐃 / University Tower 4, Noval
🚚 Or have it delivered straight to you!
✅ Why you’ll love it:
– Authentic Japanese mascarpone + hint of rhum in our tiramisu
– Banana pudding cream sourced straight from Japan
– Premium, top-quality ingredients (no shortcuts, just pure goodness!)
📩 Pasabuy now! Message us to reserve before everything’s gone.

message.text:
✨ We heard you, Tams! ✨

We’ve been a little quiet lately — kasi busy kami formulating more flavors just for you (and your cravings 🤭).
And this Monday, we’re finally dropping something NEW:
🍪 Biscoff Tiramisu — fresh, creamy, and ready to be your next favorite! 🤎
💚 This is Tamu 🍰
Your all-time cravings, made better:
🍌 Banana Pudding
☕🍫 Classic Tiramisu
🍪 Biscoff Tiramisu (NEW!)
We always listen to your suggestions, and now we’re bringing them to life — fresh batches, improved taste, and premium ingredients. ✨
⚠️ Note: We usually bake 100 pcs per week, but we can only accomodate 65 pcs only, if you’re eyeing a bulk order, message us early — slots fill up fast.
📦 Available Stocks:
– 20 pcs Classic Tiramisu (Kittii size)
- 5 pcs Classic Tiramisu (tobi size)
– 5 pcs Biscoff Tiramisu (Kittii size)
– 32 pcs Banana Pudding (Kittii size)
– 3 pcs Banana Pudding (Tobi size)
📍 Pick-up points: FEU 🐃 / University Tower 4, Noval
🚚 Or have it delivered straight to you!
✅ Why you’ll love it:
– Authentic Japanese mascarpone + hint of rhum in our tiramisu
– Banana pudding cream sourced straight from Japan
– Premium, top-quality ingredients (no shortcuts, just pure goodness!)
📩 Pasabuy now! Message us to reserve before everything’s gone.

message.text:
While Iloilo danced to the beat of the Dinagyang Festival, the Enterprise Management Society moved to a rhythm of its own. The rhythm of future founders, bold ideas, and student start-ups in the making.

We brought the enterprise energy. Every cheer, every “Hala Bira!” was a reminder that now is the best time to start something of your own.

Whether it's your first product, pitch, or pop-up idea, EMS is where FEU student entrepreneurs begin their journey. We didn’t just celebrate, We spark ambition, We plant business dreams.

The next chapter of your start-up story begins now. Be part of EMS and take that first step toward becoming your own boss.

Join the EMS community that dares to dream—and dares to do.

Membership Application:
https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zDzDiYvIP8VNj1M0cqFiMgdUN0xKMFNJTzAzNDRIQlVBU1ZRMTU0WE1IVS4u

message.text:
While Iloilo danced to the beat of the Dinagyang Festival, the Enterprise Management Society moved to a rhythm of its own. The rhythm of future founders, bold ideas, and student start-ups in the making.

We brought the enterprise energy. Every cheer, every “Hala Bira!” was a reminder that now is the best time to start something of your own.

Whether it's your first product, pitch, or pop-up idea, EMS is where FEU student entrepreneurs begin their journey. We didn’t just celebrate, We spark ambition, We plant business dreams.

The next chapter of your start-up story begins now. Be part of EMS and take that first step toward becoming your own boss.

Join the EMS community that dares to dream—and dares to do.
